Build-Depends: appstream, debhelper-compat (= 13), desktop-file-utils, gettext, itstool, ladspa-sdk, libadwaita-1-dev (>= 1.6), libbs2b-dev, libebur128-dev, libfftw3-dev, libfmt-dev, libglib2.0-dev, libgsl-dev, libgtk-4-bin, libgtk-4-dev (>= 4.10), liblilv-dev, libpipewire-0.3-dev, libsamplerate0-dev, libsigc++-3.0-dev, libsndfile-dev, libsoundtouch-dev, libspeexdsp-dev, libtbb-dev, libzita-convolver-dev, lv2-dev, meson, nlohmann-json3-dev, pkgconf
Description: Audio effects for PipeWire applications This program provides various audio effects for PipeWire applications. . This application was formerly known as PulseEffects, but it was renamed to EasyEffects after it started to use GTK4 and GStreamer usage was replaced by native PipeWire filters.
